Eskom CEO André de Ruyter is giving an update on the power utility's system challenges. Eskom announced over the weekend that stage 3 power cuts will be implemented today and tomorrow between 5 and 10pm. JOHANNESBURG - Eskom is holding a briefing on the rolling blackouts. The power utility is expected to implement stage 3 on Monday and Tuesday, at the same time. For the rest of the week, you can expect stage 2 from 5pm to 10pm. 